    "attributes": {
        "action": "Introduce measures to encourage smaller families\r\n \r\n",
        "additional_details": "This is dramatic and controversial but population growth has to stop. If not, all other \u201cgreen\u201d efforts could be in vain. Please watch the David Attenborough film. It is fascinating, beautiful, terrifying and encouraging.\r\n \r\nThe mindset of people must start to change, we need to realise the severity of this issue, people must be discouraged to have large families. Save our planet and our children.",
        "background": "The Government should introduce policies to encourage smaller families. This should include only providing child benefit and free education for up to two children and introducing an environmental tax for additional children. ",
